Sudah, ya.

292
00:21:34,041 --> 00:21:35,771
<i>Sayang!</i>

293
00:21:58,961 --> 00:22:00,771
Memikirkannya saja membuatku
merinding.

294
00:22:03,072 --> 00:22:04,201
Kamar mandi.

295
00:22:08,511 --> 00:22:09,511
Kang So Bong-ssi.

296
00:22:14,451 --> 00:22:15,451
Kenapa?

297
00:22:16,281 --> 00:22:17,281
Aku menakutkan?

298
00:22:18,652 --> 00:22:21,221
Tidak. Kenapa aku harus takut?

299
00:22:22,922 --> 00:22:25,692
Kamera tersembunyi di sini 
punyamu, 'kan?

300
00:22:31,162 --> 00:22:34,201
Uncanny valley. Itu artinya respons alami.

301
00:22:34,832 --> 00:22:39,041
Manusia merasa terhina dan kesal ketika
melihat robot yang agak mirip manusia.

302
00:22:40,541 --> 00:22:41,872
