mirip manusia...,

303
00:22:41,872 --> 00:22:43,241
...tapi aku memang sangat
mirip manusia.

304
00:22:43,642 --> 00:22:45,481
Kau pun sampai tertipu.

305
00:22:46,412 --> 00:22:47,511
Kalau begitu, selamat tidur.

306
00:22:56,761 --> 00:22:58,162
Kenapa dia itu?

307
